data.description: Welcome to this stunning single family home nestled on 1.65 acres of picturesque land, offering a tranquil setting with fantastic modern amenities in a highly sought-after location. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, this home offers ample space and a flexible layout. Upon entering, you will be greeted by an open floor plan seamlessly blending the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The gleaming hardwood floors throughout create an elegant ambiance, while the Kraftmaid cabinets in the kitchen provide both functionality and style. This home offers a large bonus room that can be customized to suit your needs, whether it be an office, playroom, or craft room. The main level master suite is truly a retreat, offering privacy and relaxation. Imagine unwinding in the luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Situated just minutes from Interstate 81 and downtown Staunton, you will enjoy easy access to an array of restaurants, shops, and amenities. After a long day, retreat to your private 12X12 deck, the perfect place for outdoor gatherings, or simply enjoying the serenity of your surroundings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours.
